Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,With that, the laundry is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what would have happened to me if I hadn't come here.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I hadn't met her...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.96,0:00:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would have...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This was an airship.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.13,0:00:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}These people were the crew.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This person was my father.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Soon, I too will...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as I said. They were completely wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.78,0:01:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the types who actually listen to advice...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.39,0:01:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...wouldn't have come here in the first place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.77,0:01:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who is that?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the fuel hasn't spilt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.73,0:01:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, it shouldn't be a problem to just leave it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.00,0:01:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A whistle?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.76,0:01:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are survivors?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.19,0:01:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You look awfully comfortable in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If you simply remain there...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll eventually be able to see your comrades again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.97,0:02:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, you'll return to the soil of the netherworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I had heard you guys could understand the common language.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.75,0:02:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If you wish to continue living, come out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well? What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! My apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.27,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You were sleeping soundly, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you having a scary dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It was scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.41,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It was scary, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.64,0:03:27.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a heartwarming dream.
